name: Ode to the River Goddess #1
description:
Ode to the River Goddess - Mixed Media work inspired by the 4th Century Chinese Poem “The Nymph of the Luo River” a story of enchantment with the goddess of the Luo River, once believed to be the daughter of an emperor who became a nymph after drowning in the river. 
Hand-Drawn Chalk Pastel combined with digital elements
